8 Craigie Circle

Cambridge 38, Mass.

21 March 1948

Dear Dean de Kiewit,

Many thanks for your kind letter. It is very interesting to hear that you have definite plans for the development of Russian studies at the University.

I entirely agree with you that courses in Russian Literature should not be limited to those given in Russ